But I do about 30 raves per year and a few festivals. I did Tomorrowland (worlds largest festival) last year in Belgium and next month I’m going Ultra Music Festival in Miami! On my 3rd rave of just February this month too 🎉
It’s the only hobby I have, costs a lot but the feeling you get at music festivals is just something else ❤️

snippet.textDisplay:
Girlll! Don’t ever fret about being 19 & single. I know you’re a wonderfully strong minded, independent young woman who’s always busy & likely doesn’t even have much time to worry about such matters, but if those thoughts ever cross your mind - banish them! You’ve got so many years ahead of you for all of that. I didn’t get my first boyfriend until I was 19, that only lasted 5 months, then my first serious partner at 21 for 18 months (knew him for 2 years prior), & although I’ve dated since I’m 33 & happily single. Sod men lol. Enjoy your younger years, live life, have a flirt, enjoy your friends (because when you’re all settled you’ll have the best memories to look back on!)
You looked stunning at the NTA’s xx
